- Federal Reserve System operates as subdivision of IMF (now central bank of world)

**Restrictions on Cash:**
- UN treaty obligated government to restrict cash use
- Every citizen issued **international ID card**
- Machine-readable cards provide positive identification at transportation depots and military checkpoints
- Used by banks and stores to access checking accounts (now called **debit accounts**)
- Cash transactions larger than five Bancors illegal in three months
- Most expenditures paid by debit card
- Only way **UN Monetary Transaction Tracking Agency (MTTA)** can combat counterfeiting and prevent money laundering
- Real targets: political dissidents and those escaping taxes in underground economy

**Ultimate Control:**
- No one allowed to earn/buy/sell without ID card
- Not allowed to leave country or migrate to another city
- If government red-flags individual, card won't clear
- Blocked from virtually all economic transactions and geographical movements
- **Ultimate control**

**No More Bank Runs:**
